snippet.title: My Racing Game is Almost Done
snippet.description:
Wishlist Apex Rush on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2638250/Apex_Rush/
Follow the development of my game here: https://discord.gg/VEMAZeD
The game is almost ready for a play test! Since last time I've added a bunch of fun jumps and loops to the map, making it more challenging and fun! 

The next episode will be the final one in this series, so it'll take some time for it to release, but make sure you Subscribe so you don't miss it!

I hope you all enjoy this video, Drop a LIKE & Subscribe if you're new! 

My Clothing Brand: https://nosleep.co/
